Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.16,0:00:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When wishing for someone else's happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone must be cursed in order to keep the balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how Magical Girls work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.27,0:00:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.62,0:00:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to Sayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.44,0:00:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.39,0:01:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you let go of my hand time will stop for you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.12,0:01:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that Witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.29,0:01:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That used to be Miki Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.74,0:01:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have witnessed that yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we running?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to run, drop what you are carrying now,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,0:01:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and go and kill that Witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.60,0:01:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't joke around!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.67,0:01:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do anything right now except get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us retreat for now.
