Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, her Soul Gem...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Sayaka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After her Soul Gem turned into a Grief Seed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a Witch was born, and she has totally disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying to me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am speaking the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the final secret hidden within the Soul Gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this jewel becomes dull and black,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we will become Grief Seeds, and then Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the inescapable fate of becoming a Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan kept saying she wanted to save the world from the hands of the Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to become a companion of righteousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:05:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She became a Magical Girl with that thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She just carried a curse that is equal to her wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more people she wanted to save, the more people she will curse now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just showing off that you know everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you have to say all that to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is Sayaka's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.76,0:05:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Sayaka's best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand everything completely now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand that all you have seen till now, has a completely different truth behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you have brought out her body, you have to treat it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you just dump it somewhere, there will be trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even still human?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come in? I have something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura-chan's words, are they true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't any error I need to rectify.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you wanted everyone to become Witches eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you let them become Magical Girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you don't misunderstand something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We mean no harm toward humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all to prolong the life of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka, have you ever heard of entropy{TLC removed: , in thermodynamics}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:07:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx95}Basically, for example, the energy obtained from a bonfire is not equal to the energy put into growing the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When changing into different forms, energy is lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The energy of the entire universe is gradually decreasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we kept trying to find a power that's not bound by the conservation of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we found, was the magic of Magical Girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.85,0:07:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We invented a scientific technique to convert the emotions of sentient creatures into energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, regrettably, we had lost our emotions long before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, we investigated the different species existing in the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and finally found you, humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering humanity's numbers and reproductive ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the emotional energy generated from one person far exceeds what's required.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your spirits are used in entropy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can each be used as a source of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, the efficiency of the transfer is the highest,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in girls who are in their second developmental stage, who change hope into despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your souls are completely lit during their transformation into Soul Gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment your Soul Gem turns into a Grief Seed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an incomparably large energy is produced.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is us, the Incubators, who are responsible for collecting this energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we all expendable to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want us to die for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how many civilizations are clashing in this universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a moment, how much energy is exhausted?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You humans will also eventually leave this planet and become our companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, you probably do not hope to receive a wilted and empty universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think of this in the long term, this is a very equal trade for all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that ridiculous reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mami-san died, Sayaka-chan has also turned into that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is too much, it's too cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only made the contract after asking for your consent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That alone should have been good enough. {[TL note: FUCK YOU FUCK YOU FUCK YOU FUCK YOU]lol Ryona}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's been deceived by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot comprehend what deception is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do not understand why it is that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when humans regret their own mistake in judgment,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they easily blame others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand what you are saying, and I can't agree with your views.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones who can't understand the values and perspective of you humans. {[TL Note: IF THAT'S THE CASE THEN SHUT UP AND FUCK OFF]think maybe Ryona is getting a little too into this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You number more than 6.9 billion now, and 10 more people are gained every 4 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you make such a fuss over losing one or two people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think that, then that shows that you are indeed our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just debating with you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish that you could understand how much good your sacrifice can be exchanged for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like I can't convince you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka, you will eventually become the strongest Magical Girl ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then a Witch most difficult to defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, we can get energy unlike anything we've received before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are willing to sacrifice yourself for the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you are welcome to find me anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're working so hard to keep the corpse fresh{or warm}. What are you trying to accomplish?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any way to get her Soul Gem back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to my knowledge, there is no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means, there are still situations that you can't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Magical Girl is an existence that transcends rationality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing surprising about Magical Girls being able to do something that transcends natural laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There has been no precedent,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I do not know what methods there might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regretfully, I cannot give you any advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell needs your help?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka-san, you don't look so good this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I just didn't sleep too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, is Sayaka-san still on leave today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go visit her later?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, is it appropriate for me to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little difficult for me to speak to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi-chan, listen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After seeing that kind of thing yesterday, you're still able to go to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to say to you, come to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi-chan, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be asking for leave today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Madoka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, do you have something to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to save Miki Sayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can she be saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she can't, will you give up on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty weird question I just asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you think that I'm an idiot,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I won't give up, until it's confirmed that she can't be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although she has become a Witch, perhaps she still remembers the voice of her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you call out to her, maybe she can summon up her memories of being a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who can do that is probably you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that really work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's why I have to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe after cleaving that Witch in two,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what would appear inside wouldn't be a Grief Seed, but Sayaka's Soul Gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those stories about love and courage defeating everything, aren't they all like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe it's because I dreamed of those stories that I became a Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I've already seen past that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka has led me back to that reason again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to come, I won't force you to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a risky move, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.41,0:14:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I can't promise that, if anything happens, I will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Kaname Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, you can sure mess up someone's rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Sakura Kyoko, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I am not feeling well. May I go to the nurse's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is the health representative for this class?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname-san also asked for leave today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the class president can accompany her...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Homura-chan come and help?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not that kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't you friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's more like being comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just banded together to defeat an enemy that we cannot defeat by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a few days, this town will welcome the "Walpurgis Night".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Walpurgis...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a terribly strong and evil Witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both she and I... probably cannot defeat it by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:16:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we set up an alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's basically just that kind of relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that really Sayaka-chan? Could it be some other Witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The style of magic is the same as yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, let me ask again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been behind everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I've never been of any use,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but please, take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a weird kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kyoko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been watching others fight, but not doing anything myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I really despicable?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want to be a Magical Girl anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just something that anyone can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You eat delicious food every day, and you have your family around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If people who live how they want become Magical Girls on a whim,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I definitely would not agree with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would beat up anyone who did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:18:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only people who have been forced into a corner would do this kind of job that disregards their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If other people wanted to try this kind of job, then they would just be looking for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe one day, you will also be forced into a situation where you must fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that time comes, then you can consider such questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Kyoko-chan{you}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She found us, she's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it like we planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan, it's Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you recognize my voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid. Continue to call out to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan, don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you, please remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan wouldn't want to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan, didn't you want to become the symbol of justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, turn back into the original Sayaka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she doesn't listen, we have the second method!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue to call out to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call Sayaka back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, stop it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan, hear us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this revenge for the battle before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that we've been fighting from the first time we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.47,0:20:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said you were too naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time, no matter how much I beat you up, didn't you stand back up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be really angry, feeling that everything I ever did was unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're no longer angry, please wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say that you believe that you can use this strength to bring happiness to people?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.49,0:21:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I have to die like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let me see the beautiful dream one more time, at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I let her come with me to do something stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.61,0:21:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In battles, don't you hate to have something weigh you down?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:22:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you protect the one you want, to protect them to the very end is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.89,0:22:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that's what I did until now too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.99,0:22:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.94,0:22:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will block this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.59,0:22:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being by yourself must be very lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I will stay with you, Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.61,0:22:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:01.73,(derp sign),,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(240,369)}{Sign}{\blur1\c&H0C0C03&}Akemi Homura
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.80,0:23:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Sakura Kyoko really have any chance to save Miki Sayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.72,0:23:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could she?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.05,0:23:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of thing is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why didn't you stop her?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she wasted her sacrifice, of course I would have stopped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time, her death has an important meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.83,0:23:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the only Magical Girl that can stand up against "Walpurgis Night" is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.64,0:23:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, if it's just you, you can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect this town, Madoka has to become a Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.67,0:23:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely won't let you get your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.15,0:23:50.45,(derp sign),,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(240,369)}{Sign}{\blur1\c&H0B0D08&}Akemi Homura
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.51,0:24:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one believes in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.29,0:24:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can stop the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.36,0:24:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't depend on anyone anymore.
